## **I’m _Naida_ , Your Photographer**

My romance with the lens began with my first point-and-shoot. I loved to
capture my sister’s smile. Since then, I’ve been creating and documenting.
Human connection moves me. I relish in the romance of French cinema. The
movement and tension that defines Dutch Golden Age art inspires me. Life,
laughter, love and light are my muse.

was full of suggestions and flexible to our baby’s schedule. Would definitely
use Naida again and again for pictures!”
